# .NET build outputs.
# bin/ contains compiled assemblies, obj/ contains intermediate build
# artifacts and NuGet restore caches; both are regenerated on every
# `dotnet build` and never belong in version control.
# Reference: https://github.com/dotnet/core/blob/main/Documentation/csharp-conventions.md
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Visual Studio / Rider local user state.
*.user
.vs/
